data.description: SELLERS MORTGAGE BALANCE IS ASSUMBABLE at 2.99% for qualified buyers! Ask for details! Lovely 3 bedroom, 2 bath POOL home on a CUL DE SAC with no immediate rear neighbors is ready for new owners. You will spend a lot of time in the backyard enjoying your LARGE SCREENED IN POOL and COVERED PATIO area. The back yard is completely fenced in and perfect for your furry family to enjoy as well! Inside, you'll love the HIGH CEILINGS with EXPOSED WOOD BEAMS and tile floors through-out all main living space and a cozy WOOD-BURNING FIREPLACE! The kitchen features WHITE CABINETS with GRANITE COUNTERTOPS and lots of functional counter work space. The kitchen, dining areas and all overlook the patio/pool area a perfect set up for entertaining!  The master suite is large and is split off in the front of the home from the other 2 bedrooms for privacy. The secondary bedrooms are on the other side of the house. All bedrooms have vinyl laminate easy care flooring. The guest bathroom has been upgraded with newer tile in the shower, vinyl flooring and upgraded vanity and it opens to the second bedroom where there is an additional vanity. Some details and upgrades not to be missed: ROOF 2013, AC 2016, WH 2021, NEW WINDOWS 2021, FULLY OWNED and paid off SOLAR PANELS that was added to the home in 2014 supplying electricity for the whole home and pool AND a decreased electricity bill! This home is ideally located just off of Red Bug Lake Rd, zoned for Top-Rated Seminole County Schools including Oviedo High School, multiple shopping and dining locations in Winter Springs, Oviedo and Winter Park areas, golf courses locations with easy access to SR 434, 436 and SR 417. Call today for your opportunity to see this home and make it yours!
